al/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthx我會繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有誤導成份<br />\n條脷擺唔啱位<br />\n練幾耐都唔得<br />\n擺得啱嘅話<br />\n試多幾次就得<br />\n所謂擺啱位<br />\n唔係話淨係頂條脷上去狂噴氣"},{"pid":"c714a27fac7fd0b90d7cefc935d212f1ebd043c8","tid":392701,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T00:05:16.000Z","msg":"獨L同電腦溝通都唔同人溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38aa607d93fd7175f15a8a71a6832a561ed58142","tid":392701,"uid":8632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nthx bro<br />\n我試左好多次都無震嘅感覺<br />\n個唇係開住咁練? <br />\n無語文天份係咪無可能練到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲氣一係漏一係谷住係入面震唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求指點</blockquote><br />\n一開始可以試下吹大力啲，未必即刻做到，平時得閒試下，一定會練到<br />\n可以參考下呢個，我都係睇呢段片練<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O7oMwO5PVbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO7oMwO5PVbg&d=VLFlM22RuJ65twpqsCwclQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b26b1a2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O7oMwO5PVbg</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我試左幾個月了 一下都震唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條脷太緊又唔得 太鬆又死 無啦無啦<br />\nBetween 啲牙係合埋？</blockquote><br />\n其實只要條脷擺啱位，你吹氣就會自動震<br />\n舌尖太前/太後都會比較難做到，大概掂到上顎有凸起嘅地方就ok<br />\n牙唔使合，好似perro咁你合埋牙就做唔到o音<br />\n唔好放棄，好多人都練好耐先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthx我會繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有誤導成份<br />\n條脷擺唔啱位<br />\n練幾耐都唔得<br />\n擺得啱嘅話<br />\n試多幾次就得<br />\n所謂擺啱位<br />\n唔係話淨係頂條脷上去狂噴氣</blockquote><br />\n未打完<br />\n你試下keep 住發普通話&quot;河&quot;個h 音<br />\n即係舌根向上頂<br />\n然後keep 住舌根位置不變<br />\n同時舌尖向上<br />\n噴小小氣唔洗多<br />\n就會震到"},{"pid":"949ed7e8a564b5382d05270e66afb72e8971d312","tid":392701,"uid":79979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T00:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如題，諗住同時學Spanish同Italian，兩個都係由零開始<br />\n<br />\n聽人講好容易混淆，但係有冇可能？有冇巴絲試過？</blockquote><br />\n唔建議,我之前懶醒學學下德文走去學埋法文,好難一時消化咁多</blockquote><br />\n本身淨想學spanish，但係太多人爭，又貪靚grade，所以reg埋italian做後備，最尾兩個都approve左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他course更加爛grade，所以想留住呢兩個course<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喔~咁你目的唔係同時精通兩個語言咁其實冇乜問題,我估你都係讀intro姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nintro同時兩個冇乜問題啦,你英文程度點?如果你英文唔差既話intro級別既野會搵到好多同英文相似既地方,唔會難<br />\n不過呢兩個語言都發音麻鳩煩,巴打擔心呢樣好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我英文算ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最難嘅rolling r都練到了，發音應該冇咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n練極都練唔到trilling r <br />\n巴打有冇咩skill指導下我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n10年前學都學唔到R音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：工聯會學"},{"pid":"0357f269948d356b5ee208ad2b42895858e8ba4f","tid":392701,"uid":8632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T00:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n喔~咁你目的唔係同時精通兩個語言咁其實冇乜問題,我估你都係讀intro姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nintro同時兩個冇乜問題啦,你英文程度點?如果你英文唔差既話intro級別既野會搵到好多同英文相似既地方,唔會難<br />\n不過呢兩個語言都發音麻鳩煩,巴打擔心呢樣好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我英文算ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最難嘅rolling r都練到了，發音應該冇咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n練極都練唔到trilling r <br />\n巴打有冇咩skill指導下我</blockquote><br />\n細過玩嘴唇，合埋口噴氣個嘴唇會震<br />\n其實原理一樣都係噴氣，不過由嘴唇變成脷<br />\n你用條脷包住上排牙後面，唔好比空氣漏出黎<br />\n咁樣<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uploa&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fuploa%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E&d=VLFlM22RuJ65twpqsCwclQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=36ae9893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/uploa&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</a><br />\nd/2017/09/09/104110_135bee7678d84e55a1b1bcef80b76bd0.jpg[/img]<br />\n再用玩嘴唇嘅方法噴氣，試多幾次就彈到條脷<br />\n我嗰陣都練左一個禮拜，一路練一路噴口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nthx bro<br />\n我試左好多次都無震嘅感覺<br />\n個唇係開住咁練? <br />\n無語文天份係咪無可能練到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n語言天份係要睇埋你點理解同記個文法structure,vocab<br />\n發音只係其中一樣</blockquote><br />\n其實發音唔太重要<br />\n俄文夠話要震脷, 但其實全俄三份之一人口都震唔到, 包括列寧</blockquote><br />\n我覺得樣樣都重要<br />\n發音==你個樣<br />\n語法==肌肉<br />\n詞彙==骨架/身高<br />\n樣樣都唔得就好似肥柒矮毒撚<br />\n生存到嘅<br />\n俾人笑咁解啫"},{"pid":"53288426a2e1ced32898d6da449d8a867a979b0e","tid":392701,"uid":7754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題，諗住同時學Spanish同Italian，兩個都係由零開始<br />\n<br />\n聽人講好容易混淆，但係有冇可能？有冇巴絲試過？</blockquote><br />\n我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e509b95085f2b761da8ec9c7c8e92e20d92a5b","tid":392701,"uid":50320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0deb187e81f3a9206bbac6726494a6f2d4748923","tid":392701,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如題，諗住同時學Spanish同Italian，兩個都係由零開始<br />\n<br />\n聽人講好容易混淆，但係有冇可能？有冇巴絲試過？</blockquote><br />\n我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打學成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好易混淆？"}]}